OL,3,CTwo commemorative services to be held
OL,4,Cmarking 52 years since Summerland fire
OL,6,FTwo commemorative services are due to
OL,7,Fbe held to mark 52 years since the
OL,8,FSummerland fire.
OL,10,FDouglas City Council will host their
OL,11,Fannual ceremony at the Summerland
OL,12,Fmemorial, while others will gather at
OL,13,Fwhat remains of the Summerland site.
OL,15,FSaturday 2 August will mark 52 years
OL,16,Fsince a fire took hold of the Isle of
OL,17,FMan's esteemed leisure complex on
OL,18,FDouglas Promenade in 1973.
OL,20,FThe blaze resulted in the death of 50
OL,21,Fpeople, with many more injured.
