OL,6,FThe following year, an investigation
OL,7,Ffound numerous flaws in the design of
OL,8,Fthe building, very little fire safety
OL,9,Ftraining by management, and the lack
OL,10,Fof escape routes.
OL,12,FA campaign formed of survivors and
OL,13,Fbereaved families are fighting to
OL,14,Foverturn the verdict of 'misadventure'
OL,15,Fplaced on those who died.
OL,17,FThey say the ruling implies those who
OL,18,Fdied were responsible for their own
OL,19,Fdeaths.
