OL,3,CTwo commemorative services to be held
OL,4,Cmarking 52 years since Summerland fire
OL,6,FAn application for a fresh inquest was
OL,7,Frecently denied by the island's
OL,8,FAttorney General, but the campaign say
OL,9,Fthey will 'continue to fight' as the
OL,10,Fanniversary approaches.
OL,12,FSurvivors, campaigners and
OL,13,Feyewitnesses from the campaign are
OL,14,Fexpected to gather on the Summerland
OL,15,Fsite from 7.00pm.
OL,17,FThe service will be opened by Ellan
OL,18,FVannin Pipes and Drums, before
OL,19,Ftributes will be paid to those who
OL,20,Fdied as a result of the fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
