OL,3,CTwo commemorative services to be held
OL,4,Cmarking 52 years since Summerland fire
OL,6,FMeanwhile at the memorial service,
OL,7,FMayor Steven Crellin will lay a wreath
OL,8,Fon behalf of the council at the Kaye
OL,9,FMemorial Garden on Queen's Promenade
OL,10,Fat 6.45pm.
OL,12,FPrayers will then be led by the
OL,13,FMayor's Chaplain, Rev Michael Brydon.
OL,15,FCouncil Leader Devon Watson said: "As
OL,16,Fa Council, we stand together in our
OL,17,Fcommitment to honour the memory of
OL,18,Fthose deeply affected by the tragedy.
